Description.value:
Quick start to develop an interface which extract contractor’s basic data from Fieldglass and create account in Concur. 
This IFLOW pulls user (contractor) data from Fieldglass through Fieldglass connector, , creates an encrypted CSV file based on Concur Employee Import 305 file schema, and uploads it to the Concur SFTP server.
